<div class="center">
  <div class="layout">
    <div class="column column_right">
      <div class="thank">
        <div class="thank__title">Your order is complete!</div>
        <div class="thank__text">We will print and ship your order on <span class="thank__bold">October 2nd, 2015!</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="column column_left">
      <div class="mark"><i class="icon icon-makes-an-impact-1"></i></div>
      <div class="progress progress_scale">
        <div class="progress__el">
          <div style="width: {{progressPercentage made_campaign.campaign_goal made_campaign.items_sold}}" class="progress__range">
            <div class="progress__tooltip">{{progressPercentage made_campaign.campaign_goal made_campaign.items_sold}}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress__label">
          <div class="progress__label-item">{{made_campaign.items_sold}}</div>
          <div class="progress__label-item">{{made_campaign.campaign_goal}}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="column column_right">
      <div class="share share_simple">
        <div class="share__text">Help us reach our impact goal by sharing this campaign with your friends:</div>
        <div class="share__list">
          <button class="share__btn"><i class="icon icon-twitter"></i></button>
          <button class="share__btn"><i class="icon icon-facebook"></i></button>
          <button class="share__btn"><i class="icon icon-instagram"></i></button>
          <button class="share__btn"><i class="icon icon-pinterest"></i></button>
          <button class="share__btn"><i class="icon icon-email"></i></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg">
  <div class="center">
    <div class="layout">
      <div class="column column_left">
        <div class="title">Order Summary:</div>
        <div class="order">
          <div class="order__id">Order ID: <span class="order__id-number">{{order.order_id}}</span></div>
          <div class="order__title-campaign">Campaign:</div>
          <div class="order__title-sub">Benefiting After-School All-Stars</div>
          <div class="order__list">
            <div class="order__item">
              <div class="order__preview"><img src="assets/img/product.jpg" alt="" class="order__pic"></div>
              <div class="order__info">
                <div class="order__name">Men’s T-Shirt</div>
                <div class="order__options">Heather Grey - L</div>
                <div class="order__price">$18.00</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="order__item">
              <div class="order__preview"><img src="assets/img/product.jpg" alt="" class="order__pic"></div>
              <div class="order__info">
                <div class="order__name">Men’s T-Shirt</div>
                <div class="order__options">Heather Grey - L</div>
                <div class="order__price">$18.00</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="order__stats order__stats_thin">
            <div class="order__stats-value">$3.00</div>
            <div class="order__stats-title">Sales Tax:</div>
          </div>
          <div class="order__stats order__stats_thin">
            <div class="order__stats-value">$4.00</div>
            <div class="order__stats-title">Shipping:</div>
          </div>
          <div class="order__stats order__stats_total">
            <div class="order__stats-value">$43.00</div>
            <div class="order__stats-title">TOTAL:</div>
          </div>
          <div class="order__stats order__stats_thin">
            <div class="order__stats-value">$3.00</div>
            <div class="order__stats-title">Payment method:</div>
          </div>
          <div class="order__stats order__stats_thin">
            <div class="order__stats-value">**** 9452</div>
            <div class="order__stats-title">Card number:</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column column_right">
        <div class="title">Shipping Address</div>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Orders begin shipping October 2, 2015</p>
          <p>{{order.first_name}} {{order.last_name}}
          <br>{{order.shipping_address.address1}} {{order.shipping_address.address2}}
          <br>{{order.shipping_address.city}}, {{order.shipping_address.state}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="title">Contact Support</div>
        <div class="content">
          <p>If you have any questions, please feel free to contact our customer support team by emailing us at <a href="mailto:support@omaze.com">support@omaze.com</a>. We will be in touch as soon as possible!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
